id: S02-T2-ParserService
title: Totem Data Parser Service
status: pending
type: feature
requires:
  - NODE_EXPRESS
---

## Objective
Build the services necessary to traverse the instance directories and parse Markdown/YAML files into structured data.

## Requirements
- Create a new file `server/src/services/totemParser.ts`.
- Implement `parseProjectConfig(path)` using the `yaml` package to read `project.config.yml`.
- Implement `parseSprintFile(path)` to extract goals, tracks, and tasks from `.ptl` files.
- Implement `parseTaskFile(path)` to extract task metadata (status, ID, type) from `.pd` files.
- Handle graceful degradation if certain files are missing.
